snippet.description: Here we've picked our five favorites across every style and category, but if you already know which

snippet.title: Making headphones mono
snippet.description: If you want to listen to your music in mono there are couple of options available including software tweaks and headphone adapters, as Geoffrey Morrison explains.

snippet.title: V-Moda Remix Remote in-ear headphones
snippet.description: The V-Moda Remix Remote headphones earn our Editors' Choice recommendation with a colorfully dynamic sound profile, a generous two-year replacement warranty, and a handful of accessories that ensure a tight seal and versatile usability.

snippet.title: Beats Studio Wireless Headphones
snippet.description: While it'll cost you a hefty $380, the Beats Studio Wireless is an excellent wireless Bluetooth headphone.

snippet.title: Superlux HD681 headphones
snippet.description: Despite atrocious cosmetic qualities, the insanely cheap Superlux HD681 headphones have a sound that aspires to greatness and only narrowly misses the mark.

snippet.title: Sony MDR-7506 headphones
snippet.description: They've been around since 1991, but the Sony MDR-7506s are still great sounding -- and fitting -- headphones for less than $100.

snippet.title: Sony MDR-V6 headphones
snippet.description: They may be close to 30 years old, but the comfortable fitting Sony MDR-V6s are arguably the best-sounding headphones for under $100.

snippet.title: Headphone buying guide
snippet.description: In-ear vs. on-ear, circumaural vs. supraaural, open vs. closed back -- shopping for the right pair of headphones can be tough, but CNET's on the job with a buying guide to help you narrow down your choices.

snippet.title: V-Moda XS on-ear headphones
snippet.description: If you're looking for a $150-$250 on-ear headphone, the well-built V-Moda XS should be on your short list.

snippet.title: GoGroove BlueVibe DLX Bluetooth headphones
snippet.description: There's nothing terribly special about the GoGroove BlueVibe DLX, but it's an affordable wireless Bluetooth headphone that will be "good enough" for people on tighter budgets.
